1.1.1.name: wordpress/social-juggernaut
1.1.1.description:
This plugin was designed with ease-of-use in mind. The coding used is very basic, so edits are not hard. I will be updating in the future with updates that I feel necessary as well as user-suggested edits. Some topics I want to address:

  • Drag and Drop order of Icons
  • Verify URL input
  • Update with more icons

I would really appreciate feedback regarding the plugin. I will be updating the icons available on a weekly basis, and I rely on you guys to suggest appropriate updates.

  • Twitter - @Paul_Ruescher
  • Website - http://www.juggernautwebsites.com/social_juggernaut/
